commit.message: Added a way to switch between scenes

Merge branch 'react' of github.com:zuhairp/LearningSpace into react
Add form validation and styling for entering Quizlet set ID
first push: created mountain scene (sky no color)
Add options screen that transitions to vr screen
Move VR into a separate scene for SPA routing
Add module to get terms from Quizlet Sets
Add module to call arbritary WebTasks

Add a WebTask.io script for Quizlet API

The Quizlet API does not use the correct CORS headers which makes it
difficult to call from a browser with default security. In order to
abide with security policy, the webtask calls the quizlet from outside
the browser context and then passes on the results with the correct CORS
headers necessary. A workaround that works
